gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 123, Wizards 108
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz defeated the Wizards, 123-108. Lauri Markkanen led the way for the Jazz with 29 points and a season-high six 3PM, while John Collins added 22 points and 16 rebounds in the victory. Kyle Kuzma tallied 26 points, six rebounds and five assists for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Jazz improve to 23-23 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 7-37.
